Common.SpaceDescription.Common.Text: Reception, conference room, 3 offices, open area, kitchen
Reception, conference room, 1 office, kitchen. Industrial build out.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
+  Located in the Park at Broken Sound overlooking the 13th hole of Broken Sound Golf Club

+  6 residential projects with 1,642 multifamily units

+  The Boca Raton Tri-Rail Station is only one mile away with a shuttle stop directly in front of The Atrium

+  Town Center Mall, Park Place Center, Downtown/Mizner Park, Interstate 95 and Florida’s Turnpike are nearby

+  Minutes from Boca Raton Executive Airport and situated between Palm Beach International Airport and Fort Lauderdale/Hollywood International Airport

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
+  Three-story atrium with skylight at the center of the building creates stunning natural light and open-air effect

+  Some vacant spaces are in shell condition to allow for tenant finish flexibility

+  Class A finishes throughout 

+  Spectacular golf course views

+  Underground parking garage with executive reserved parking

+  Upgraded tenant storage units and picnic area with gazebo

+  Building offers a fully redundant backup generator for all tenant spaces

+  Free WiFi in the common areas

+  Security cameras and card key access system
